1 yield spread premiums, servicing release premiums, and financial
2 counseling fees; and[. "Total net income" ]
3 3. Does not include:
4 a. Interest on the mortgage loan itself;[,] or
5 b. Fees paid to compensate unaffiliated third parties[; and
6 (b) "Total loan amount" means the amount financed in the mortgage loan less the
7 total net income generated by the originating licensee or person, or the
8 affiliate of the originating licensee or person].
9 Section 2. This Act applies to contracts entered into on or after the effective
10 date of this Act.
